Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:29.70,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}{\fad(0,40)}I Love You Miss Mystery  hate no nai rabirinsu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:36.25,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}Kono ai o dakishimete ima nazo o tokiakashite
